429
00:22:02,020 --> 00:22:04,650
Go sleep at home if it’s noisy.

430
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:06,820
Come on!

431
00:22:06,820 --> 00:22:08,410
Keep working!

432
00:22:36,460 --> 00:22:37,700
