468
00:25:02,260 --> 00:25:03,610
You drank again?

469
00:25:04,940 --> 00:25:08,410
Yeah, with my friends in a bar.

470
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:10,090
Where is he?

471
00:25:11,220 --> 00:25:12,260
He went to hospital for medicine,

472
00:25:12,260 --> 00:25:13,330
and let me talk with you.

473
00:25:16,390 --> 00:25:17,110
You got injured, too.

474
00:25:17,110 --> 00:25:18,420
Why didn’t you go for medicine?

475
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:19,370
No need.

476
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:21,390
Get up.

477
00:25:21,390 --> 00:25:22,260
You need some medicine.

478
00:25:22,260 --> 00:25:23,700
You make people worry about you.

479
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:24,460
