545
00:30:08,260 --> 00:30:10,300
To affect justice with public opinion

546
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:11,500
is impossible.

547
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:12,130
You...

548
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:14,420
We can

549
00:30:14,420 --> 00:30:15,850
drop the charge.

550
00:30:16,350 --> 00:30:18,420
And we can talk about the compensation.

551
00:30:18,420 --> 00:30:20,490
It’s nothing about the compensation.

552
00:30:20,490 --> 00:30:22,010
The truth is what we want.

553
00:30:22,010 --> 00:30:23,540
Dr. Wen did nothing wrong...!

554
00:30:25,980 --> 00:30:28,090
I’ve learned about your demand.

555
00:30:28,830 --> 00:30:30,090
We’ll respond to the complaint.

556
00:30:30,220 --> 00:30:32,550
I’m sure your unreasonable demands

557
00:30:32,550 --> 00:30:33,820
